description: {"blocks":[{"key":"aqsmk","text":"The described protocol was used to confirm that NADPH-cytochrome P450 reductase from Helianthus annuus was N-glycosylated when recombinantly expressed in Pichia pastoris (Komagataella phaffii).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":85,"length":18},{"style":"italic","offset":107,"length":2},{"style":"italic","offset":154,"length":16},{"style":"italic","offset":171,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

status.info: We use this protocol and it's working

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"1kpuj","text":"12,5 µl of yeast lysate containing sufficient amount of target protein for detecting by Western analysis was pipetted into a tube. Two samples were prepared in parallel, one for negative control without N-glycosidase and the other with PNGase F.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":203,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"burh5","text":"0,5 µl of 10% sodium dodecyl sulfate (SDS) and 1 µl of 1M dithiothreitol (DTT) were added.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"39msh","text":"The mixtures were cooled to room temperature after which 2 µl of 0,5 M Tris-HCl, pH 8 and 2 µl of 10% Triton X-100 were added.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"13bml","text":"2 µl of PNGase F (500 U/ml) was added to one of the samples. Instead of N-glycosidase, water was added to the negative control sample.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":72,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8tcpo","text":"SDS-PAGE sample buffer was added and the samples were heated for 5 min at 99 °C. SDS-PAGE and Western analysis were carried out to see whether the molecular weight of the target protein had decreased.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
